Frances Morris (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frances_Morris_(actress) 0 Frances Morris (August 3, 1908 – December 2, 2003) was an American actress. Born in 1908 in Springfield, Massachusetts, she died in Santa Clarita, California, in 2003. Frances_Morris ( August_3_,_1908 – December_2_,_2003 ) was an_American_actress .
